# Livskompassen — Cursor Rules

Kanon ligger i **`.cursor/rules/`** (MDC). Kärn-invariants: **`.cursor/index.mdc`** (always-on, ~300 tokens).

## Snabbindex

| Zon | Auto-attached regel | Globs |
|-----|---------------------|-------|
| UI / Obsidian Calm | `design-calm.mdc` (kanon), `ui-design.mdc` (pekare) | `src/**/*.tsx`, `src/**/*.css` |
| ADK & synapser | `synapser-adk.mdc` | `functions/src/adk/**`, `functions/src/triggers/**` |
| RAG & silos | `memory-silo.mdc` | `functions/src/lib/*Rag*.ts` |
| Säkerhet & WORM | `security-firestore.mdc` | `firestore.rules`, `functions/**`, `sharedRules.ts`, `DCAP.ts` |
| Locked UX | `locked-ux-features.mdc` | Valv, Familjen, Barnporten, Planering |
| Android | `android-capacitor.mdc` | `android/**`, Capacitor-auth |

## 3-zonsystem (routing)

- **Hjärtat** `/hjartat` — Dagbok, Speglar; Valv via `/valvet` (PIN, plausible deniability)
- **Vardagen** `/vardagen` — MåBra, Planering, Ekonomi, Arbetsliv
- **Familjen** `/familjen` — Barnfokus, Livslogg, Barnporten, Trygg Hamn

Legacy-rutter (`/dagbok`, `/valv`, `/mabra`, `/planering` …) omdirigeras — skapa inga nya utanför 3-zonsystemet.

## Vid stor ändring

1. Läs [`docs/specs/modules/Arkiv-GAP-REGISTER.md`](docs/specs/modules/Arkiv-GAP-REGISTER.md)
2. Fas 19+ körplan: [`docs/evaluations/2026-06-15-fas19-masterplan-v2.md`](docs/evaluations/2026-06-15-fas19-masterplan-v2.md)
3. Deploy: `npm run smoke:predeploy` → YOLO GO → Pontus OK

Design-detaljer (färger, typografi, Tailwind): se `design-calm.mdc` — **inte** duplicerade här.
